<span class="postbody"><span style="font-weight:bold">Evita5</span>, <table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr><td><span class="genmed"><strong>Цитата:</strong></span></td></tr><tr><td class="quote">
<br />
