<span class="postbody"><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr><td><span class="genmed"><strong>Наталья Ризаева писал(а):</strong></span></td></tr><tr><td class="quote"><span style="font-weight:bold">Maxim000</span><IDXSKIP>, 
